{
  "stem": "24614.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there is one place there that those who were killed during the war in-- are buried on one-- in one grave.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My daddy has, though, a separate grave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because we reburied him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he has a stone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember my mother saying, now I can die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] We needed mon-- sorry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- first of all, my, my younger brother, Elie-- my younger brother-- my only brother who was with me in hiding-- he, he really didn't want to live.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wanted to go outside and be killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to say, why do I have to live?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want it anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't take it-- day and night in a little room, not allowed to even talk loud, and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother used to say, Kinder, children, [GERMAN SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We must live so we can retell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The world won't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the meantime, when my daddy died, my mother lost hope of living, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother was a big smoker then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She smoked cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember my mother used to say, I don't want food today.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I want a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember rolling cigarettes for my mother, the tobacco and the thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "How she finally got those things, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But she had a cigarette rolling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When daddy died, she stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She didn't ask for that cigarette.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were very much concerned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because we knew that if mother doesn't want to smoke, she's very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She's not going to live.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I remember after a week-- or I don't know how many days, because the days went into nights, the nights went into days-- she said, Clara, roll me a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that was one of my beautiful things in hiding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My mother asked for a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
